<%= callout("NB", " These are notes from the discussion on Friday!", :small) %>

### All

* Don't interrupt each other
* Let everyone speak and make their points
* Be professional, respectful, attentive, engaged
* Realize that people are different, have different backgrounds, situations and ability
* Do what you can to allow everyone to contribute

### Teachers

* All homework assignments should be on the Latte page, their dates should be correct and consistent across all resources
* Make all class materials, notes, videos, etc visible to students
* Class: Start on time, finish On Time, don't forget to fit in a break
* Professor should be interactive with the students (Teachers)
* Return graded work promptly (our policy is within 1 week)

### Students

* Class: Show up on time
* Team meetings: show up on time, complete your commitments
* Do the work, stay up to date, so you can contribute to the class and to your team

### Consensus

* Everyone agree?
* Anyone disagree?
* Do we have a consensus?

